<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>AI Experience Study</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-center">
    <div class="card text-center">
      <h1>Welcome to this Study</h1>
      <p>This research examines how people's experiences with AI tools relate to their everyday decision-making styles. The study takes approximately 15–20 minutes.</p>
      <p>All your responses are completely anonymous and will be used solely for academic research.</p>
      <% if (error) { %><div class="error"><%= error %></div><% } %>
      <form action="/join" method="POST" class="mt-24">
        <label class="field-label">Your Prolific ID</label>
        <input type="text" name="prolific_id" value="<%= prefill %>" placeholder="Enter your Prolific ID" required autocomplete="off">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-full mt-16">Begin Study</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
